short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows Nektarstock users to retrieve sales data from their agencies.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows Nektarstock users to retrieve sales data from their agencies. If a user wants to use our analytics.nektarstock.com analytics tool to analyse their performance across agencies, user has to install the Nektarstock extension.
